---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navigation from '../../components/Navigation.astro';
---

<Layout title="Brand Identity & Design - Two Ghosts Strategy">
  <Navigation />

  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-10 py-10">
    <div class="section-heading relative mb-8">
      <div class="bgtext-section">Visual Systems</div>
      <h1 class="section-title">
        Brand Identity & Design
      </h1>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 space-y-16">
      <!-- Section 1 -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
          Visual Identity That Reinforces Strategy
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-xl text-gray-50">
          <p>
            Design without strategy is decoration. And most brand design is exactly that—pretty pictures that don't connect to anything meaningful.
          </p>
          <p>
            Real brand identity work starts with strategy: who you are, what you stand for, and how you want to show up. Then we translate that into a visual system that's distinctive, flexible, and actually usable.
          </p>
          <p>
            We don't do trendy design that looks dated in six months. We build brand systems that have staying power—that look professional without being boring, distinctive without being weird, and polished without being corporate.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 2 -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
          What We Do
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-50 mb-6">
          We design comprehensive brand identity systems that bring your strategy to life across every touchpoint.
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-3 text-xl text-gray-50 ml-6">
          <li>Logo design and visual identity</li>
          <li>Brand style guides and design systems</li>
          <li>Color palette and typography systems</li>
          <li>Icon libraries and illustration styles</li>
          <li>Marketing collateral and templates</li>
          <li>Website design and UI systems</li>
          <li>Packaging and product design</li>
          <li>Environmental and experiential design</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 3 -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
          Who This Is For
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-xl text-gray-50">
          <p>
            Companies starting from scratch or fixing what's broken. Teams with a strong brand strategy that needs visual expression. Leaders who know that brand design is more than making things pretty.
          </p>
          <p>
            If you're ready for a brand identity that works as hard as your strategy—let's design it.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class="text-center mt-12">
        <a
          href="/schedule"
          class="btn-gradient inline-block px-8 py-3 text-white font-black rounded-full"
        >
          Let's Talk Strategy
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="container-80 py-12 border-t border-gray-800 mt-16">
    <div class="text-center text-gray-400">
      <p>&copy; 2025 TWOGHOSTS, LLC. All Rights Reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>
